            "extra_id": 0x46,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "All right, I think we got enough of them."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x4a,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Well, we worked really hard today!<CR>Now, let's go see Boss."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Regina, you sure have a lot of stamina... I can't move anymore..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x4c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Ayesha, you can't be worn out from this."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "C'mon, stand up straight. If you want, I'll help you up, but..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x8,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "I might accidentally touch you in some weird places... Hmhmhm..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "No, no, I'll do it myself."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x195,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "All right, good job!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x9,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Ayesha, why don't you become a<CR>prospector, too? You might<CR>become as robust as me!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Hmm...I do admire you quite a bit,<CR>but I don't think I could do that..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x20e,
            "name_id": 0x24,
            "extra_id": 0x1f8,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "Now, I'll announce the results.<CR>After a fair and accurate count..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x20e,
            "name_id": 0x24,
            "extra_id": 0x1f9,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "The one who got the most number of<CR>slags was...the duo of Regina and<CR>Ayesha!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x49,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "Yaaay! The prized alcohoool!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "Whew, I'm glad we worked so hard."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x20e,
            "name_id": 0x24,
            "extra_id": 0x1f9,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "Good job. I can really count on you, Regina."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x20e,
            "name_id": 0x24,
            "extra_id": 0x1fe,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "Here's the money and my prized alcohol. Take them, you little lasses!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x4c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "Thanks, Boss! I love you!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x20e,
            "name_id": 0x24,
            "extra_id": 0x1f9,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "Goodness, you're too friendly, strong, and generous... You're gonna make me worry."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x20e,
            "name_id": 0x24,
            "extra_id": 0x1fa,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "If you don't calm down, you'll never find a husband."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x8,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "I don't caaarrre. If that's the case, I'll just take Ayesha as my bride!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x38,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "Wha‐!?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x20e,
            "name_id": 0x24,
            "extra_id": 0x1f7,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "Missy, you have rather nice skills, too. You'd make a nice partner for Regina."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x20e,
            "name_id": 0x24,
            "extra_id": 0x1fb,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "How about it? Wanna switch teams?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3a,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "S-Switch teams?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "I'm not really thinking about getting married or anything yet..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x20e,
            "name_id": 0x24,
            "extra_id": 0x1f7,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "Don't get so flustered, it's not like that. I'm talking about prospecting. You're one funny missy..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x9,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "msg_string": "Boss, I'm not too fond of you trying to indiscriminately recruit every young person you see..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0xc,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1b,
            "msg_string": "Plus, I have a prior appointment with Ayesha, so you can't have her!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x8,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1c,
            "msg_string": "Here, Ayesha, the money's for you!<CR>And I'll take the alcohol!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x9,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1d,
            "msg_string": "I'm gonna drink yummy alcohol today! Let's have a drink, Ayesha!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1e,
            "msg_string": "I'll just keep you company.<CR>Well, shall we go?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0xffffffff,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xffffffff,
